                        <div class="tool-info">
                            <h2 class="tool-title">ContentKeeper Blocker</h2>
                            <p class="tool-description">
                                ContentKeeper Blocker filters or blocks inappropriate content, used in schools and workplaces 
                                to enhance productivity and safety. This comprehensive web filtering solution automatically 
                                categorizes and restricts access to non-educational websites, social media platforms, and 
                                potentially harmful content. The system typically deactivates after school hours, allowing 
