                        <li><strong style="color: #eab308;">Medium Risk:</strong> Content filtering and blocking with scheduled operation times, moderate data collection</li>
                        <li><strong style="color: #22c55e;">Safe:</strong> Background device management with minimal user interaction and limited data scope</li>
                    </ul>
